Focus Entertainment and Saber Interactive are excited to celebrate the release of the Siege Update for their blockbuster third-person shooter Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2. Available now for free to all Xbox Series players, this new update comes with a new PvE game mode and two new cosmetics DLCs for Season Pass owners.

author: Warhammer
description:
Not one, but two titans are on the table today with the gigantic constructs known as Cathayan Sentinels, which stand tall in the face of Chaos. Dan is going through a pair of paint schemes in the name of the Celestial Dragon, with these terracotta and warpstone variants!

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Terracotta Sentinel 

Contrast:
Cygor Brown
Guilliman Flesh
Iyanden Yellow

Base:
Zandri Dust 

Layer:
Pallid Wych Flesh

Shade:
Berserker Bloodshade

Technical:
Contrast Medium

Warpstone Sentinel 

Base:
Abaddon Black
Caliban Green
Corvus Black 

Layer:
Moot Green
Skavenblight Dinge
Warpstone Glow

Technical:
Lahmian Medium

Tools:
L Drybrush STC
M Base Brush STC 
M Drybrush STC 
M Shade Brush STC
S Layer Brush STC

If you're new to painting, our Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
